description:
Anarchy token is a ERC-20 Hyper-deflationary token experiment.

There are other tokens of this genre, but many are too boisterous in supply.

Anarchy fixes this with a 500 token supply, 18 decimals, and a 5% burn rate.

With the initial supply being 100% airdropped, the experiment will be fast acting.

Most other Hyper-deflationary tokens may take months to years to see scarce supply.

With Anarchy Token, scarce supply will be seen within weeks.

No Dev with major holdings.

100% community owned.
name: Anarchy token
